%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ftax%2Fextension.htm%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4bHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=e368e1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.ird.gov.hk/chi/tax/extension.htm）。</a><br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年4月9日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間21時45分"},{"pid":"ef2c1142f3cc6909ec301480494e9b3f8658f3bc","tid":1991021,"uid":185734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"系統無 update ，係咪要照交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75837ccb0cf5526bd0974ffc4fb8523e2728f50","tid":1991021,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:07:56.000Z","msg":"交左objection慢慢等<br />\n有排都未做到你果份"},{"pid":"69e8763c790d7afc1082e51a9b620fb41e781b41","tid":1991021,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T12:20:33.000Z","msg":"政府wfh 丫嘛<br />\n我今日下午打去都無人聽電話"},{"pid":"95e103b843ea80d9bc571934cccdd3cbcda5a78d","tid":1991021,"uid":129924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99fa7795a1529e219cc9f83e7e74bbb8bbcee593","tid":1991021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"係咪即係唔撚駛交住？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紓緩措施：繳稅限期自動延期三個月<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  行政長官於昨日（四月八日）宣布，為紓緩企業和個人因2019冠狀病毒病所帶來的財政負擔和現金流，於本年四月至六月到期繳交的2018/19課稅年度薪俸稅、個人入息課稅及利得稅的稅單，繳稅限期自動延期三個月。<br />\n<br />\n  稅務局今日（四月九日）公布有關安排，如薪俸稅、個人入息課稅及利得稅納稅人早前已依期繳交了2018/19課稅年度稅單的第一期稅款，第二期稅款的繳稅限期將由稅單上列明的日期自動順延三個月。<br />\n<br />\n  上述紓緩措施不適用於須在離港前清繳稅款的人士、繳納物業稅的納稅人，以及已獲批准分期繳稅的納稅人。<br />\n<br />\n  相關示例及常見問題已上載稅務局網頁（<a href=\"http://www.ird.gov.hk/chi/tax/extension.htm）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ird.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Ftax%2Fextension.htm%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4bHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=e368e1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.ird.gov.hk/chi/tax/extension.htm）。</a><br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年4月9日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間21時45分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-2